Version 1.0beta1 - released 2014-10-11
* lifted requirements to CMSimple_XH >= 1.6 and PHP >= 5.0.0
* added support for CMSimple_XH 1.6 APIs
* added image filenames as titles to image-picker (suggested by svasti)
* added German manual
* added Danish translation (contributed by maeg)
* added version.nfo for hi_updatecheck

